com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.collect

Class AbstractHashStruct<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.collect.AbstractHashStruct<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the key type
    V - the value type

    public abstract class AbstractHashStruct<K,V>
extends Object
    This is a base utility used to build hashing data structures similar to that of HashMap and HashSet.

    By default, this will have a resizing threshold of 14 items, which can be changed using #setResizeThresh(int) and a hashing strategy defaulted to .AbstractHashStruct.HashStrategy#A_TROLL that can be changed using #setStrategy(com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.collect.AbstractHashStruct.HashStrategy)

    Benchmarks for all 3 hash strategies can be found here

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    AgentTroll
